    public static enum LCNSyntax.DataType
extends java.lang.Enum<LCNSyntax.DataType>
    Describes different types of data.
    V = Tvar
    TA = Temperature variable
    TB = Temperature variable
    SA = Current setpoint of controller 1
    SB = Current setpoint of controller 2
    LO = Lux at T-Port (old)
    Since:
    1.7.0
    Author:
    Patrik Pastuschek
